      "span_text": "To illustrate the application of these methods to research, a set of key processes was selected that serve as intermediate outcomes for overall clinical trial success ( Table 2). We then discussed the identification of change strategies that draw on insights garnered from prework, the application of standard \"change concepts, \" 19 or the work of others that has successfully improved a similar process."
